{
  "stem": "27335.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He always jumped the first, and when we was over, and then he indicated come on-- come on, follow me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it's true that that's how it happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then when she had to go to the bed first, she was a little trembling, like a-- like a really [? donkey. ?] [LAUGHS] She didn't know what to expect, because she was-- you read it-- you read it in her-- in her diary how all the boys that were swarming around-- around her in the kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so many of them, mind you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some-- some were very serious, that in some-- some-- in some places she indicates in her-- in her diary she was almost raped by-- you could-- you could feel it.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And somehow because of this-- of this forcefulness.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So made-- made her more-- more rigid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because she-- she looked for things up here first.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's what she-- she wanted to be sure who the man is before she opens herself for physical.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But unfortunately all we had three times.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then one day I was going up to the-- to the club.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they told me, well, she's not in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She's out somewhere.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it was nothing [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She might be called-- called in for-- for a briefing, or some kind of a quick lecture for some information, connection with the-- with the mission and so on.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When the second day she's not there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Third day I went up and then I looked for the-- for the man who was-- who was the chief among them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And among the-- well the 22, 7 of them were-- were Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Most of them-- most of them from-- from Romania, from Transylvania, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I ask him [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
